        {
            "name": "Fetchling",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [
                {
                    "name": "Masters of Adaptation",
                    "type": "section",
                    "text": "Kayals understand that many Material Plane cultures view them with suspicion or even fear, and take pains to adapt to cultures with which they seek to establish trade. Unfortunately, kayals' mastery at cultural adaptation can often backfire, leading to fears that the so-called \u201cfetchlings\u201d are an invading force that seeks to duplicate and replace those with whom they merely wish to do business.",
